Everybody knows about the competitive history between this and A Bug's Life, but what does Nostalgia Critic think of DreamWorks' first animated film? Let's take a look at Antz.

Check out our store - https://channelawesome.myshopify.com/

Support this month's charity - https://solvecfs.org/

Antz is a 1998 American animated adventure comedy film directed by Eric Darnell and Tim Johnson and written by Todd Alcott, Chris and Paul Weitz. Produced by DreamWorks Animation and PDI, the film features the voices of Woody Allen, Sharon Stone, Jennifer Lopez, Sylvester Stallone, Christopher Walken, Dan Aykroyd, Anne Bancroft, Danny Glover and Gene Hackman.
